{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2558","heading":"National military associations: assistance at national conventions","label":"2558 National military associations: assistance at national conventions","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2558","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptIV/ch152","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2558","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2000— renumbered as this section.Pub. L. 106–398section 2548 of this title","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 101–189, div. A, title III, § 329(b)103 Stat. 1417Nov. 29, 1989“Section 2548 [now 2558] of title 10, United States Code, as added by subsection (a), shall take effect on the date of the enactment of this Act [].”Nov. 29, 1989"],"amendments":["Amendments2000— renumbered as this section.Pub. L. 106–398section 2548 of this title","Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 101–189, div. A, title III, § 329(b)103 Stat. 1417Nov. 29, 1989“Section 2548 [now 2558] of title 10, United States Code, as added by subsection (a), shall take effect on the date of the enactment of this Act [].”Nov. 29, 1989"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Authority To Provide Services","label":"a .—Authority To Provide Services","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2558/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2558","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2558%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of a military department may provide services described in subsection (c) in connection with an annual conference or convention of a national military association.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Conditions for Providing Services","label":"b .—Conditions for Providing Services","identifier"